OL,3,CMurder investigation underway after
OL,4,Cman found dead in Bracknell
OL,6,FA murder investigation is underway
OL,7,Fafter a man was found dead in
OL,8,FBracknell, Berkshire.
OL,10,FPolice were called to the Market
OL,11,FStreet area at around 11.40am on
OL,12,FSunday (26 April) to reports of a
OL,13,Fdeceased man in his thirties.
OL,15,FHis next of kin have been informed,
OL,16,Fhowever formal identification is yet
OL,17,Fto take place.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
