OL,3,CMurder investigation underway after
OL,4,Cman found dead in Bracknell
OL,6,FThree men aged 35, 27 and 33 all from
OL,7,FBracknell, have been arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of murder and assault by
OL,9,Fbeating.
OL,11,FOfficers are in place at Gowring House
OL,12,Fservice yard in the town centre and
OL,13,Fwill remain there for some time.
OL,15,FDetective Superintendent Kevin Brown,
OL,16,FHead of the Major Crime Unit said:
OL,17,F"Our thoughts remain with the man's
OL,18,Fnext of kin following his death.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
