PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777363547
OL,3,CMurder investigation underway after
OL,4,Cman found dead in Bracknell
OL,6,F"We are in the early stages of a
OL,7,Fcomplex investigation, and we are
OL,8,Ffollowing several lines of enquiry to
OL,9,Festablish the full circumstances
OL,10,Faround the murder.
OL,12,F"Members of the public are likely to
OL,13,Fsee an increased police presence in
OL,14,Fthe area while we investigate, and we
OL,15,Fwould advise anyone with any concerns
OL,16,Fto please speak to one of our
OL,17,Funiformed officers."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
