CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777363547
OL,3,CMurder investigation underway after
OL,4,Cman found dead in Bracknell
OL,6,F"I would ask that at this time people
OL,7,Frefrain from speculation on social
OL,8,Fmedia or other mediums whilst we
OL,9,Finvestigate to find the truth behind
OL,10,Fthis incident and loss of life. I
OL,11,Fwould also ask that if anyone has
OL,12,Finformation regarding the
OL,13,Fcircumstances of this offence to make
OL,14,Fcontact with us as soon as possible".
OL,16,FAnyone with information around the
OL,17,Fincident is being asked to contact 101
OL,18,Fquoting reference 43260203481.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@dO]
